==English==

===Adjective===
'''binomial''' 

# Consisting of two terms, such as [[genus]] and [[species]].

===Noun===
{{wikipedia}}
'''binomial'''
# {{algebra}} A [[polynomial]] with two terms.
# {{algebra}} A [[quantity]] expressed as the [[sum]] or [[difference]] of two terms.
# {{biology}} A [[scientific name]] at the rank of species, with two terms,  e.g. ''Cannabis sativa''. In particular in formal names of plants, fungi and bacteria. 

